data.description: Welcome to this move-in ready beauty in Silverleaf Village! This exquisite two-story home offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and serene lakeside living. With 2,045 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, this home offers ample room for relaxation and entertaining. Step inside this 3BR/2.5BA home and be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an inviting and spacious atmosphere perfect for entertaining. The main level features a large living room, awash in natural light and beautiful views of the lake. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, offering stainless appliances, sleek countertops, plenty of cabinets and a generous sized pantry for all of your cooking gadgets. The breakfast bar is the perfect spot for guests to gather while you cook. Whether you're preparing a quick meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary creativity. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, offering stainless appliances, sleek countertops, plenty of cabinets and a generous sized pantry for all of your cooking gadgets. The breakfast bar is the perfect spot for guests to gather while you cook. Whether you're preparing a quick meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary creativity. On the main level, you'll also find the master bedroom, a private oasis designed for comfort and tranquility. With an en suite bathroom, complete with a fully tiled shower, dual vanity and walk-in closet, the master suite offers a soothing retreat after a long day. Venture upstairs to discover an 18x12 loft-style family room, and two generously sized bedrooms, providing comfortable accommodations for family members or guests. Outside, the beauty of nature unfolds before your eyes. Sliders off the living room open to the spacious backyard with beautiful views of the lake. There's plenty of room for backyard bar-be-ques, gardening or a game of catch and the community offers an array of resort-like amenities with multiple pools including an adult pool, lap lane pool, spray park, pavilions, a field house, dog parks, pickleball and tennis courts, miles of sidewalks and trails and much more...see you there!
